WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:00:03.820 --> 00:00:08.200
From 1930s rural Australia comes The  Valley Between.

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:20.940
It's getting nearer!

00:00:20.940 --> 00:00:22.340
Let's split up!

00:00:23.320 --> 00:00:25.180
Hurry up, hurry!

00:00:25.180 --> 00:00:27.340
Get up the tree, get up the tree!

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:31.580
What are we going to do now?

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:35.640
The Valley Between.

00:00:35.740 --> 00:00:42.960
The story of a German immigrant family adjusting to life on the land in their new, and sometimes strange world.

00:00:53.300 --> 00:00:54.220
What's happening?

00:00:54.220 --> 00:00:58.620
14-year-old Bruno Gunto takes us on a personal voyage of discovery.

00:00:58.620 --> 00:01:03.580
Caught between his parent's old world Lutheran values and the prospect of adventure,

00:01:03.580 --> 00:01:07.020
Bruno always manages to find himself in trouble.

00:01:08.680 --> 00:01:10.360
Bruno, stay away from me!

00:01:10.520 --> 00:01:12.260
Emma, don't you dare!

00:01:13.540 --> 00:01:17.500
I'm not going to the picnic if I have to wear this! I'd rather stay at home and...

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:18.180
Good!

00:01:18.880 --> 00:01:20.520
Stay home then.

00:01:23.820 --> 00:01:25.760
He's just upset. It's nothing.

00:01:25.760 --> 00:01:29.620
He isn't a little boy anymore.
He's just behaving like one.

00:01:33.480 --> 00:01:38.780
Stop! Stop!
Stop the train!

00:01:38.780 --> 00:01:39.900
Brake!

00:01:44.140 --> 00:01:47.280
Go! Run hurry, run for your life!

